pick up a knife from the coffee table.
while holding the bread, look around the room.
walk around the room with the bread.
come back to the coffeetable and stand there.

turn around and look at the wall, then back to the coffee table.

Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right to face the bread.
Cut the bread into slices with the knife.
Move left to face the coffeetable.
Put the knife on the coffeetable.
Move right to face the coffeetable.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.

Cool the bread slice in the fridge and take the bread out.

Take the knife from the top of the table.
Move nearer to the bread which is on the table.
Make the bread into slices.
After that, move little bit left side of the coffeetable.
Put the knife on the coffeetable.
move little bit right side of the coffeetable
Take a single slice of the bread.
Take left turn, walk straight and take a right turn and walk towards the fridge and enter into it.
Open the fridge and place the bread slice inside the fridge and close the door. After some minutes, open the door and take out the bread and close the door again.

Place the bread slice on the top of the sidetable.
